text: Çatal is a Turkish word meaning "fork". It may refer to: *Çatal railway station, a station in İzmir Province, Turkey *Çatalhöyük (also Çatal Hüyük/Höyük), an archaeological site in Konya Province, Turkey ;Catal and Čatal *Čatal Česjma, a water spring in the Republic of Macedonia ==See also== * * *Catalan (disambiguation)
title: Çatal
